name: SXZ Blood Elves [ Warcraft ]
description:
All the content I make is and will be completely free on CivitAI.
But if you want to support me with a coin, then you can do it here.

Trained on AbyssOrangeMix2 with Clip Skip 2.

Sample images was generated with Luma and AOM2

Recommended embeddings:
1. easynegative
2. bad-hands-5
3. badhandv4

Strength 0.5-0.8 is optimal.

PLEASE CHECK YOUR LORA NAME AFTER DOWNLOAD.

Male Blood Elf: 1boy, hebelf, athletic
Female Blood Elf: 1girl, shebelf, athletic

Eye color: green, blue, yellow, purple, red

Also you may improve it with glowing eyes

When you using 1boy, hebelf or 1girl, shebelf add opposite in negative prompt.
